<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<manifest xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android" android:versionCode="1" android:versionName="-debug" package="net.protyposis.android.spectaculumdemo.debug" platformBuildVersionCode="22" platformBuildVersionName="5.1.1-1819727">
	<uses-sdk android:minSdkVersion="16" android:targetSdkVersion="22" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.INTERNET" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.CAMERA" />
	<uses-feature android:name="android.hardware.camera" android:required="false" />
	<uses-feature android:name="android.hardware.camera.autofocus" android:required="false" />
	<application android:theme="resourceId:0x7f080000" android:label="Spectaculum Demo Debug" android:icon="res/mipmap-mdpi-v4/ic_launcher.png" android:debuggable="true" android:allowBackup="true">
		<activity android:label="Spectaculum Demo Debug" android:name="net.protyposis.android.spectaculumdemo.MainActivity">
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="android.intent.action.MAIN" />
				<category android:name="android.intent.category.LAUNCHER" />
			</intent-filter>
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="android.intent.action.VIEW" />

				<data android:scheme="http" android:host="*" android:pathPattern=".*\.webm" />
			</intent-filter>
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="android.intent.action.VIEW" />
				<category android:name="android.intent.category.DEFAULT" />
				<category android:name="android.intent.category.BROWSABLE" />
				<data android:mimeType="video/*" android:scheme="file" />
				<data android:mimeType="video/*" android:scheme="content" />
			</intent-filter>

		<activity android:label="VideoView (Android API) Demo" android:name="net.protyposis.android.spectaculumdemo.VideoViewActivity" />
		<activity android:label="MediaPlayer (Android API) Demo" android:name="net.protyposis.android.spectaculumdemo.MediaPlayerActivity" />

		<activity android:label="Camera Demo" android:name="net.protyposis.android.spectaculumdemo.CameraViewActivity" />
		<activity android:label="Image Demo" android:name="net.protyposis.android.spectaculumdemo.ImageViewActivity">

				<action android:name="android.intent.action.VIEW" />

				<data android:scheme="http" android:host="*" android:pathPattern=".*\.jpg" />
				<data android:scheme="http" android:host="*" android:pathPattern=".*\.png" />
				<data android:scheme="http" android:host="*" android:pathPattern=".*\.bmp" />

			<intent-filter android:label="Spectaculum Demo Debug">
				<action android:name="android.intent.action.VIEW" />
				<category android:name="android.intent.category.DEFAULT" />
				<category android:name="android.intent.category.BROWSABLE" />

				<data android:mimeType="image/*" android:scheme="content" />

		</activity>
